title: A Grandpa for Christmas 2007 Hallmark HDTV.x264-REGRET
description:
A Grandpa for Christmas



After his estranged daughter is hospitalized, eighty-year-old Bert Riley takes Becca, the granddaughter he never met, under his wing. The young girl proves to be a catalyst in bringing the family together, repairing the wounds of the past, and making bright new memories for Christmas.

Stars: Ernest Borgnine (Golden Globe Nomination for this role), Katherine Helmond, Jamie Farr and Juliette Goglia.




Original Air Date: 24-Nov-2007
